Pedro Henrique Lima and Junior, Pedro Manoel Galetti and Macario, Phoeve and {de Oliveira Fratoni}, Rafael and Meurer, Rafael and {Saint-Clair}, Rafael S. and Romagna, Rafael Spilere and Lacerda, Raquel Caroline Alves and Cerboncini, Ricardo Augusto Serpa and Lyra, Ricardo Brioschi and Lau, Ricardo and Rodrigues, Roberta Costa and Faria, Rog{\'e}rio Rodrigues and Laps, Rudi Ricardo and Althoff, S{\'e}rgio Luiz and {de Jesus}, Shayana and Namba, Sumiko and Braga, Talita Vieira and Molin, Tamara and C{\^a}mara, Thanyria P. Fran{\c c}a and Enedino, Thayz Rodrigues and Wischhoff, Uschi and {de Oliveira}, Vanessa Cristina and {Leandro-Silva}, Victor and {Ara{\'u}jo-Lima}, Vitor and {de Oliveira Lunardi}, Vitor and {de Gusm{\~a}o}, Reginaldo Farias and {de Souza Correia}, Joz{\'e}lia Maria and Gaspar, Lucas P. and Fonseca, Renata Cristina Batista and Neto, Paulo Affonso Fonseca Pires and {de Aquino}, Ana Carla Medeiros Morato and {de Camargo}, Bruna Betagni and Cezila, Beatriz Azevedo and Costa, Leonardo Marques and Paolino, Roberta Montanheiro and Kanda, Claudia Zukeran and Monteiro, Erison C. S. and Oshima, J{\'u}lia Emi F. and {Alves-Eigenheer}, Milene and Pizo, Marco Aurelio and Silveira, Lu{\'i}s F. and Galetti, Mauro and Ribeiro, Milton Cezar},
  year = 2019,
  journal = {Ecology},
  volume = {100},
